videos.headline: Smith powers in for Irish TD
videos.description: Jahmir Smith bulldozes his way through the Louisville defense to reach the end zone and give Notre Dame a 7-0 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Smith powers in for Irish TD) 2019/9/2

videos.headline: Louisville's Dawkins makes difficult 1-handed catch
videos.description: Seth Dawkins bobbles a pass with one hand to make a difficult grab along the sideline for an 18-yard gain.

videos.headline: Pass runs for 8-yd Louisville TD
videos.description: Jawon Pass rolls out and scurries to the end zone to score an eight-yard Louisville touchdown and tie the game at 7-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pass runs for 8-yd Louisville TD) 2019/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pass sneaks in for 2nd rushing TD
videos.description: Jawon Pass slips through the Notre Dame defense to score a 17-yard touchdown and give Louisville a 14-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Pass sneaks in for 2nd rushing TD) 2019/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Notre Dame's Jones scores TD to tie game
videos.description: Tony Jones Jr. takes the handoff and score an 11-yard Notre Dame touchdown to tie the game at 14-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Notre Dame's Jones scores TD to tie game) 2019/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Irish take the lead on Book's rushing TD
videos.description: Ian Book gives Notre Dame the lead before halftime with an 11-yard touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Irish take the lead on Book's rushing TD) 2019/9/2

videos.headline: Cardinals and Irish have difficulties hanging onto the ball
videos.description: Late in the second quarter, Notre Dame and Louisville trade turnovers on three consecutive possessions.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Cardinals and Irish have difficulties hanging onto the ball) 2019/09/02 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Book connects with Tremble for Irish TD
videos.description: Ian Book completes a pass to Tommy Tremble, who reaches paydirt for a 26-yard Irish touchdown and a 28-14 lead over Louisville.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Book connects with Tremble for Irish TD) 2019/09/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Book leads Notre Dame past Louisville
videos.description: Louisville gives Notre Dame a challenge for much of the first half, but Ian Book leads the No. 9 Fighting Irish to a 35-17 victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Book leads Notre Dame past Louisville) 2019/09/02 ESHEET SOTFULL
